{"tid":424734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再取消4班機,稱個別事件","createTime":"2017-10-05T04:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T06:26:56.000Z","uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7fbb8de759196f53f7cec89a0897cff5e7f215c","tid":424734,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"昨日中秋節，香港快運除取消了早前已公佈的5個往返大阪、名古屋、首爾航班之外，再取消4班往返東京、峴港及張家界的航班，事件引起HK Express苦主關注組不滿。香港快運發言人表示，受到安全培訓部門導師離職影響，只取消18班航班，而昨日額外取消的4航班只屬個別事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171005/20173138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171005%2F20173138&d=qm%2FEjCb%2BruC%2FKbOXS6utqNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9a4b38e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171005%2F20173138&h=295d98d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171005/20173138</a>"},{"pid":"451882f9304c9760cb5b577a15189115d2e3b35f","tid":424734,"uid":62121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"慣撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢無機取消先係個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e3ffdfd99a852aa1a679a38d54496c3eb8a6e2","tid":424734,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"支那海南航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}